title: Eddie Murphy to receive top US humor prize at Kennedy Center
text: > Top News Eddie Murphy to receive top US humor prize at Kennedy Center FILE - In this Feb. 22, 2015 file photo, Eddie Murphy presents the award for best original screenplay at the Oscars at the Dolby Theatre in Los Angeles. Chris Rock, Kathy Griffin, Arsenio Hall and other leading comedians will perform Sunday, Oct. 18, in honor of Murphy as he receives the nationâ€™s top prize for humor, the the Mark Twain Prize for American Humor, at the Kennedy Center in Washington. (Photo by John Shearer/Invision/AP, File)
